#

Stuffed Bell Peppers with Rice and Black Beans

45 min
$10
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyHealthyQuick Meal

Description

Colorful bell peppers filled with a savory mix of rice, black beans, and spices make for a nutritious and delicious meal!

Ingredients

  • bell peppers: 4
  • cooked rice: 1 cup
  • canned black beans: 1 can (15 oz)
  • corn (frozen or canned): 1 cup
  • diced tomatoes (canned): 1 can (14.5 oz)
  • cheddar cheese (shredded): 1 cup
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • chopped cilantro (optional): for garnish
